const actionType ={
    fetchProducts : 'FETCH_PRODUCT',  
    filterProducts : 'FILTER_PRODUCT',  
    filteredProducts : 'FILTERED_PRODUCT',  
    increase : 'INCREASE',
    decrease : 'DECREASE',
    showCart : 'SHOW_CART',
    addToCart : 'ADD_TO_CART',
    removeFromCart : 'REMOVE_FROM_CART'
}


export default actionType;
